"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-news-ap-paris-flavor-flav-public-enemy-olympics-b2543133.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Maggie Steffens asked for more support for the U.S. women's water polo team, and the captain received one particularly surprising response.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maggie Steffens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From a clock-wearing rap icon.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moved by Steffens' Instagram post,Flavor Flavhas stepped forward to help the U.S. team as it goes for an unprecedented fourth consecutive gold medal at theParisOlympicsthis summer.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.31252640925826e-27, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is finalizing a deal that will make him a USA Water Polo sponsor and the official hype man for a program seeking a bigger spotlight.\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 65-year-old Flav, a founding member and hype man withPublic Enemy, has jumped headfirst into his new duties, highlighting some of the team's best players on social media.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also is making plans to watch the women's team play in Paris.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.343469633355233e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I come out and I watch this water polo team ... 'USA!\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"USA!'\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yo, I am going to be the biggest hype man that they ever had in their life,\\\" he told theAPon Friday.\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to be bigger than any cheerleader that they had in their life.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to cheer this team on, and I am going to cheer this team into winning a gold medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Winning has been the usual result for the U.S. women's team since the 2012 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it has not attracted the same attention or support as similarly dominant American programs, largely because water polo remains a niche sport throughout most of the world.\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9995833341425779, \"rank\": 0.00029182530217190225, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That - along with a little nostalgia - prompted Steffens, 30, the last remaining member of the 2012 team, to post on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1795, \"end\": 1804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.31252640925826e-27, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While expressing gratitude for the opportunity to play and her love for her sport, she also encouraged anyone reading the post to check out her team and highlighted the constant financial struggle for most Olympic athletes.\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have gotten a lot of comments you know of 'Oh, it's so cool what you have done.\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bummer you are not a soccer player or a basketball player, because your team would be getting way more publicity or way more support,'\\\" Steffens said Friday from Paris, where the team is on a training trip ahead of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.343469633355233e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And instead we are still kind of where we were at 12 years ago, which for me is not my goal.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have always wanted to propel the sport forward.\\\"\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enter Flav, who was inducted with the group Public Enemy into the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame in 2013.\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2535, \"end\": 2547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Enemy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2438978591992542e-15, \"text\": \"Public Enemy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Enemy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Enemy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flav's manager brought the post to his attention, and he decided he wanted to help.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One thing about me, I know what it feels like to want to see a dream come true,\\\" said Flav, who is known for wearing a big clock on a chain around his neck.\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know what it feels like to want to achieve a goal, and I am the type of person that, if I see you trying, then I am going to do whatever I can to help you.\\\"\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steffens said it was \\\"very surreal\\\" when Flav - whose legal name is William Jonathan Drayton Jr. - reached out.\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3082, \"end\": 3089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Ealing\", \"score\": 0.9997834267696367, \"rank\": 0.00021662011898190283, \"text\": \"Drayton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Ealing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Ealing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked what she knew about Flav and Public Enemy before the connection, Steffens promptly imitated Flav's frequent \\\"Flavor Flav!\\\"\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"declaration.\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steffens is one of the oldest players on the U.S. team, but she said Ryann Neushul, 24, had Public Enemy in her top five on the music streaming service, Spotify.\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3344, \"end\": 3356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Enemy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2438978591992542e-15, \"text\": \"Public Enemy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Enemy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Enemy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A couple of the team's coaches and Steffens' family also were excited about the partnership.\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My whole family was like 'Is this real?\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Flav is part of the water polo world now?'\\\"\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steffens said.\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was like 'I do not know what's going on, but I want to wear a clock right now and that's how I am feeling.'\\\"\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steffens and the U.S. team also have another high-profile supporter in Taylor Swift.\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3792, \"end\": 3804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7055331279369542e-43, \"text\": \"Taylor Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They had plans to see the musician's Eras Tour concert on Friday night at La D\\u00e9fense Arena - the venue for the women's water polo final on Aug. 10.\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Women's national team manager Ally Beck reached out to Swift's camp and surprised the team with the tickets.\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 4063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3990, \"end\": 3994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beck\", \"score\": 0.9999808581187057, \"rank\": 1.9142247801026583e-05, \"text\": \"Beck\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beck\"}, {\"begin\": 4010, \"end\": 4015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999999979722816, \"rank\": 1.7226569589523065e-09, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flav said he also contacted Swift's team, but the tickets had already been approved.\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4092, \"end\": 4097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999999979722816, \"rank\": 1.7226569589523065e-09, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flav, who is working on another tour with Public Enemy that could begin later this year, then held up a T-shirt with his picture that read \\\"KING SWIFTIE.\\\"\", \"from\": 4150, \"to\": 4304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4192, \"end\": 4204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Enemy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2438978591992542e-15, \"text\": \"Public Enemy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Enemy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_Enemy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am proud to support Taylor.\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"...\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Flavor Flav is a Swiftie, the king of all the Swifties,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4341, \"to\": 4406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's another connection Flav has with his new favorite team.\", \"from\": 4408, \"to\": 4470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"___  AP Summer Olympics: https://apnews.com/hub/2024-paris-olympic-games  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4477, \"end\": 4479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.999999999953161, \"rank\": 4.7012348553352054e-11, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}]}"